{
  "stem": "942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so when we were finished working, in the evening, the SS guards, to have fun with us, they allowed us to run into these ponds that were not far from there, to wash ourselves off.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So what they did is they unleashed these big guard dogs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they sicced them on us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we ran like crazy, into the water, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And if a bunch of people jumped on you, you know, you could, you could drown, you know, under the weight of these people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So-- but I was able to-- I was able to swim.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I remember one day I swam into the reeds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I found two duck eggs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because there were some ponds there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were raising ducks somewhere, not far from there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I found these two duck eggs in this reed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that, I thought, was a great find.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I remember, I had one egg right away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I thought, I'll bring the other one back to camp and give it to my father and uncle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was just-- I want to backtrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We worked together for quite a while, with my father and uncle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But they realized that as soon as the kapos or the SS commandant, who was the commandant of our group.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I remember his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "His name was scharfuhrer, which is sergeant, Scharfuhrer Kunz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He was an Austrian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "This man was about six foot four, a very skinny type of a guy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He was-- he had his pistol was always hanging down from his belt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as soon as they noticed that there was a family connection, a father and a son, they would start to beat one or the other.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they did not want to have anything like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
